file = {:Users/Takuto/Dropbox (追手門学院)/アプリ/Mendeley/pdf/PLoS ONE/Matsunaga et al/Genetic variations in the human cannabinoid receptor gene are associated with happiness/Matsunaga et al. - 2014 - Genetic variations in the human cannabinoid receptor gene are associated with happiness.pdf:pdf},
